# @atlys/design-system is a PRIVATE package and is intentionally NOT yet listed
# in package.json so the project installs cleanly out of the box (the UI uses a
# token-accurate local stand-in in components/ds.tsx).
#
# To use the real design system:
#   1) Configure the registry + auth below (example shows GitHub Packages).
#   2) `npm i @atlys/design-system` and import its styles.css in app/globals.css.
#   3) In components/ds.tsx, switch the re-exports from the local stand-in to
#      `export { Button, Card, Text, Select, TextArea, Modal, Spinner } from "@atlys/design-system";`
#
# @atlys:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com
# //npm.pkg.github.com/:_authToken=${NPM_TOKEN}
